FBIS4-43941 "drweu121_j_94005" FBIS-WEU-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Milan Court Acquits Former Foreign Minister Milan Court Acquits Former Foreign Minister LD2206140694 Rome RAI Uno Television Network in Italian 1130 GMT 22 Jun 94 LD2206140694 Rome RAI Uno Television Network Italian BFN [Excerpt] Gianni De Michelis, the former foreign minister, has been acquitted by the Milan court. He faced a charge of violating the law on the public financing of parties in connection with 144 million lire paid by the Acqua company which were used to pay his secretaries. [passage omitted
